{"tid":2388452,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"花冤枉錢「清槍」！雞排妹純愛杯遭控太貴　超低成本價曝光","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T11:10:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b342563bc01568bf0ee368b47f1848c838d5a83","tid":2388452,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"「雞排妹」鄭家純30日凌晨在臉書透露，在主持尾牙時，遭主辦老闆性騷擾，沒想到卻遭陳沂質疑「利用廠商炒新聞」，她也不忍在臉書開炮，原本的性騷擾事件，卻延伸變成「雙姝對決」，就在雞排妹回擊後，陳沂啟動大砲模式，狂在臉書上發文，更掀起雞排妹先前出的飛機杯，被網友在PTT抱怨「售價怎麼賣得比募資便宜」，讓陳沂狠酸：「賣到快兩千就是在買一個意淫的感覺啊。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/30/3006961-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F30%2F3006961-PH.jpg&h=3e4e7ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲雞排妹的純愛杯遭質疑「價格詐騙」。（圖／翻攝自雞排妹IG、資料照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/01/2965013-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F01%2F2965013-PH.jpg&h=e922d939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有PTT網友PO文抱怨，在募資期間訂了雞排妹的飛機杯，本來說11月會出貨，沒想到12月中還是沒收到貨，令他傻眼的是，本來只想查一下出貨進度，竟看到本來標榜未來會賣2540元的飛機杯，募資期間打7折變1780元，沒想到官網上竟只賣1700元，比他先買的1780元還便宜，讓他大呼：「說好的未來售價2540呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/31/3008369-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F31%2F3008369-PH.jpg&h=a2ab2802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陳沂狂酸雞排妹。（圖／翻攝自陳沂臉書）<br />\n<br />\n對此，陳沂立刻開砲「這就是我說我最討厭的做生意不誠實」，她直言飛機杯是不能真的用陰道去灌膜的，因為矽膠進入陰道會死人，所以只有工版，大陸製作成本價大概一百左右，讓她直嗆雞排妹，「一個飛機杯日本製進口來也頂多五六百，賣到快兩千就是在買一個意淫的感覺啊」。"},{"pid":"f705eb4f4bfeba8defdb107b327f20b869da038e","tid":2388452,"uid":7043,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:52:34.000Z","msg":"有牌子貴D唔係正常嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e449ae9132ad44c1a22a3f3bf25ef594defefae6","tid":2388452,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同香港鬥黃理由一樣"},{"pid":"799e758e9d1661d9e8b41d63d76cb8f3ec2b8f70","tid":2388452,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:57:20.000Z","msg":"其實台灣點解會叫&quot;飛機杯&quot;, 台灣明明將打飛機叫打手槍, 但點解飛機杯又會跟香港叫法"},{"pid":"1b281d3fa05dbc2846efa5c19c90f25f45233407","tid":2388452,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:59:30.000Z","msg":"模個閪出面，幾時要你入面紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4f186f56efda1ed968e64d390d835f03288a1b","tid":2388452,"uid":382334,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"男人做到咁真係好樣衰，想省錢用手啦，左手右手輪住黎囉，買咩杯"},{"pid":"5653980b13b4c1f918d802f91ac10035c5336bd0","tid":2388452,"uid":143321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"名牌袋成本都好平<br />\n點解賣十幾萬？"},{"pid":"7a192a2b7431ba0342519d7fad94de305ac50c49","tid":2388452,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5653980b13b4c1f918d802f91ac10035c5336bd0","tid":2388452,"uid":143321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"名牌袋成本都好平<br />\n點解賣十幾萬？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「成本平」係萬能key嚟<br />\n明買明賣 冇呃冇騙 有咩問題？"},{"pid":"ef485893e3e17653bfa574ffd75feea7525e3f2b","tid":2388452,"uid":338262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"呃錢爛膠"}]}